    "creation_date" : 1422526050,
    "answer_id" : 28211896,
    "question_id" : 28211806,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javaee/7/api/javax/persistence/criteria/ParameterExpression.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>ParameterExpression</code></a>. Note: <em>Untested</em>.</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>CriteriaBuilder cb = entityManager.getCriteriaBuilder();\nCriteriaQuery&lt;Long&gt; cq = cb.createQuery(Long.class);\nRoot&lt;MyEntity&gt; from = cq.from(MyEntity.class);\ncq.select(cb.count(from));\nParameterExpression&lt;Integer&gt; p = cb.parameter(Integer.class);\nq.where(cb.eq(from.get(&quot;age&quot;), 45));\nreturn entityManager.createQuery(cq).getSingleResult();\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.objectdb.com/java/jpa/query/jpql/where\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Reference</a>.</p>\n"
