    "body" : "<p>The best and simple way in jpa :</p>\n\n<pre><code>public interface YourEntityRepository extends JpaRepository&lt;YourEntity, Serializable&gt; {\n\nLong countByAgeGreaterThan(Integer age);\n\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
