    "question_id" : 28211806,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you use <code>EntityManager.createQuery()</code> instead of the CriteriaBuilder it looks like this:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>final TypedQuery&lt;Number&gt; query = em.createQuery(&quot;SELECT COUNT(e) FROM MyEntity e WHERE e.age = :age&quot;, Number.class);\nquery.setParameter(&quot;age&quot;,45);\nfinal long count = query.getSingleResult().longValue();\n</code></pre>\n"
