  "title" : "How to count number of rows using JPA?",
  "body" : "<p>I try to count number of rows using JPA.I want to use where clause \nhowever I can't. </p>\n\n<pre><code>CriteriaBuilder qb = entityManager.getCriteriaBuilder();\nCriteriaQuery&lt;Long&gt; cq = qb.createQuery(Long.class);\ncq.select(qb.count(cq.from(MyEntity.class)));\ncq.where();  //how to write where clause \nreturn entityManager.createQuery(cq).getSingleResult();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>How can I set where clause forexample where age=\"45\".\nThanks in advance.</p>\n"
